{"id": "zorgondernemers-afwachtend-met-bedrijfsopvolging__a2-late-chunking__0023", "text": "In the coming years, the sector will change to provide more care with fewer resources. The demand for care continues to increase due to an aging population, while it is hardly possible to attract more healthcare personnel. Innovation and collaboration make work easier and more fun, ensuring that healthcare provision remains sustainable and of high quality.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "zorgondernemers-afwachtend-met-bedrijfsopvolging__a2-late-chunking__0023", "source_slug": "zorgondernemers-afwachtend-met-bedrijfsopvolging", "source_title": "Healthcare entrepreneurs are waiting for business succession", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/sectorprognoses/healthcare/zorgondernemers-afwachtend-met-bedrijfsopvolging.html", "source_date": "2025-12-05", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "sectorprognoses", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 23, "n_chunks_total": 31, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 23}}
